# Use uv-native tooling
Use `uv add` and `uv sync` for dependency management. Never use `requirements.txt`, `pip`, `uv pip`; do not use anything pip-related.

Run tests and linters with `uv run ruff --fix...`, `uv run mypy...`, `uv run pytest...` etc.
